A change history search that is based on a date range defined in days returns different results depending on the time zone you're in.  At the moment, this query returns 22 results for GMT-8 and 13 for GMT+1:

{code}
project = JRA and status changed to Resolved after -3d
{code}

Changing this to hours reports the same number of results for both time zone:

{code}
project = JRA and status changed to Resolved after -72h
{code}

I have reproduced this on JAC (6.0m2) and SAC (5.2)

