You have to go to the design view.  And, when using the design view, the popup modals are small and it's easy to forget to save/update your changes when you cannot see it in the modal popup.  Since other modals automatically accept changes (there is no specific save), individuals don't know to do that and can lose their changes or not understand why something isn't working.

